and it seems to help.</i>

45:01.156 --> 45:04.743
Enjoy your booty bumps,
you absolute train wrecks.

45:06.245 --> 45:07.955
<i>Some people want to rot.</i>

45:07.955 --> 45:13.001
<i>♪ It must be exhausting
Always rooting for the anti-hero... ♪</i>

