45:30.936 --> 45:34.148
-  ...five, four, three...
-  <i>None of them</i>

45:34.148 --> 45:35.441
<i>have any idea who she once was.</i>

45:35.441 --> 45:37.151
<i>She's just their most devoted teacher.</i>

45:37.151 --> 45:38.819
Ready or not, here I--

45:39.945 --> 45:44.283
