<i>Tom Lockwood was right.</i>

46:26.909 --> 46:28.327
<i>You can come home again.</i>

46:28.911 --> 46:30.704
<i>All you need is Kate,</i>

46:30.704 --> 46:34.166
<i>plus a cybersecurity team,
a squadron of publicists, and Cynthia.</i>

46:34.166 --> 46:37.794
<i>Scrub search results, hack news archives,
bribe the Madre Linda chief of police,</i>

46:37.794 --> 46:41.340
<i>all to support
the simple, true story of Joe Goldberg.</i>

46:42.132 --> 46:45.093
Your story is incredible.
You must be tired of talking about it.

46:45.093 --> 46:49.848
People are curious, I understand,
but it's-- It is pretty simple.

46:50.557 --> 46:54.436
Many people have lived
through violent partners.

46:54.436 --> 46:57.189
My late wife, Love, was deeply troubled.

46:57.189 --> 46:59.358
I just did my best.

46:59.942 --> 47:03.487
<i>Public consensus is, I made the sensible
choice to put my son in safe hands.</i>

47:03.487 --> 47:08.325
Well, not to blow smoke, but you're sort
of a quiet hero here and back in the UK.

47:08.325 --> 47:10.410
Oh, I wouldn't say that.

47:10.410 --> 47:12.955
Were you yourself shocked
when you read of your own death?

47:16.041 --> 47:19.127
<i>My favorite's when they ask about
the DNA mix-up involving some toes,</i>

47:19.127 --> 47:22.881
<i>but Cynthia's right to steer us
to less sensational waters.</i>

47:22.881 --> 47:24.508
Let's move back to Kate.

47:27.010 --> 47:29.763
As you're grieving your dad,
you've stepped into his shoes,

47:29.763 --> 47:33.350
- kept the company running smoothly.
- I've had help.

47:33.350 --> 47:35.727
Is that how you see your role, Joe?
Supportive boyfriend?

47:35.727 --> 47:38.689
Only because I haven't been able
to convince her to elope yet.

47:38.689 --> 47:40.607
Shocker, this woman is busy.

47:40.607 --> 47:43.402
Says the man who spontaneously
bought a book shop, darling.

47:43.402 --> 47:45.529
It was closing down.

47:45.529 --> 47:49.449
Books are a passion of mine.
We should be talking about the foundation.

47:49.449 --> 47:51.577
It's what this is all for,
after all.

47:51.577 --> 47:55.622
Plan's ambitious, an arts school
here and London, and by year's end?

47:55.622 --> 47:57.624
Well, I don't mind pushing hard.

47:58.375 --> 48:00.711
If you're looking for the core
of Kate Lockwood, that's it.

48:01.545 --> 48:02.921
She's a fighter.

48:02.921 --> 48:04.423
Oh, I think we both are.

48:07.968 --> 48:09.636
All for the good, of course.

48:11.138 --> 48:14.766
I can make this work for all of us.

48:17.603 --> 48:20.105
I've done bad things.

48:20.981 --> 48:21.982
I'm not proud.

48:23.817 --> 48:26.528
But the important part is,
I've been given a chance to redeem myself

48:26.528 --> 48:28.071
and make up for what I've done.

48:28.071 --> 48:34.202
And I can only imagine
how that must sound to you, really.

48:34.202 --> 48:35.203
I--

48:35.203 --> 48:38.707
I promise, no one has to get hurt.

48:40.751 --> 48:41.585
Nadia.

48:45.464 --> 48:47.633
- No, no, no!
- Shh. Nadia.

48:49.051 --> 48:51.011
<i>I got a second chance.</i>

48:51.011 --> 48:54.097
<i>And this time, I'm utilizing all of me.</i>

48:56.183 --> 48:57.684
Give me your hand.

49:00.020 --> 49:01.104
Give me your hand.

49:07.444 --> 49:08.278
Nadia.

49:10.405 --> 49:14.242
Tell them all about me.
No one's gonna believe Dexter.

49:14.242 --> 49:15.994
So you'll live.

49:15.994 --> 49:18.622
You're right, I want that for Dexter.

49:18.622 --> 49:22.834
Honestly, my greatest pride as a teacher
is that I could help you grow.

49:25.921 --> 49:29.966
And there's gonna be a box
found in your bedroom by the police.

49:31.176 --> 49:33.345
Rhys Montrose's things. Anonymous tipster.

49:35.055 --> 49:36.306
They'll realize it was Eddie.

49:37.766 --> 49:38.850
That's why you killed him.

49:42.104 --> 49:43.772
You have so many gifts.

49:45.816 --> 49:47.609
I'm looking forward
to watch what you do next.

49:55.992 --> 49:58.370
<i>She refused to speak in her own defense.</i>

49:58.995 --> 50:01.039
<i>Still hasn't spoken from prison.</i>

50:02.124 --> 50:04.668
<i>Like I said, smart.</i>

50:18.515 --> 50:20.225
See, I'm simply very lucky.

50:20.851 --> 50:24.020
Don't give me points for coffee. That's
insulting, not in front of a journalist.

50:25.439 --> 50:26.982
<i>I get it now.</i>

50:26.982 --> 50:29.651
<i>Love can be real, complete.</i>

50:30.902 --> 50:34.197
<i>- If you are.</i>
- So, what's next for the power couple?

50:34.865 --> 50:38.201
Well, at the risk
of sounding terribly sincere,

50:38.827 --> 50:41.371
we're largely focused
on changing the world.

50:41.371 --> 50:43.832
<i>So many ways to do that.</i>

50:43.832 --> 50:45.959
- Hmm.
-  <i>I have so many tools now.</i>

50:45.959 --> 50:50.213
<i>Sure, killing's one of many,
but it's not a one-size-fits-all solution.</i>

50:51.131 --> 50:53.884
She's here to change the world.

50:53.884 --> 50:58.180
<i>Though the killing part
is also much easier now.</i>

50:59.014 --> 51:01.141
<i>But I'm honest with myself about it.</i>

51:01.141 --> 51:03.226
I'm just here to help.
